Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞠户上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全机 散开！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为对方采取雷电攻击的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在切换期间会出现空隙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 不会那么容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.69,0:00:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来的话…还有什么其它的应对手段吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞠户上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.96,0:00:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Deucalion来电
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.59,0:00:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令部下达了撤退命令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.95,0:00:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退？全军撤退吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.92,0:00:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dales小队和Orlov小队应该也接到了命令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.72,0:00:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤！快撤！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dales-22！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人…敌人在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.82,0:00:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚没有被我们打倒的那架透明的重甲骑兵去那边了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.78,0:01:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Clydesdale队长呼叫Orlov队长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能听到我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.69,0:01:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是Orlov队长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.15,0:01:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.75,0:01:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.53,0:01:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里…已经只剩下…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.99,0:01:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷击和透明…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还有一架…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.38,0:01:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传令给他们 继续攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将敌人包围全歼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟拉姆公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.26,0:01:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我尽最大努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这已经是极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了 斯雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.13,0:02:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:52.19,OPJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}君の手が広げた　何もない空よ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:57.82,OPJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}理屈の海だけの　解を遊べば
